    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>QMU is committed to maintaining the highest standards of research integrity and therefore complies with the Universities UK Concordat to Support Research Integrity. This concordat seeks to provide a comprehensive national framework for good research conduct and its governance.</p>]]></Value>
